Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}喂 大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}看我不戳瞎你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}变态大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们很明显就是佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过 只要给你吃一发雷枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这热风能把射出去的雷枪都吹飞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}康尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}吸了口气 烧伤了喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没事 只是被雷枪的碎片划伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}比起这个 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}找到反击的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\bord3\shad3\fsp0\an3\1c&H0080FF&\b1}{\u1}现在可以公开的情报\N\N超大型巨人的热风\N{\r\fs16\bord3\shad3\fsp0\an3\1c&H0080FF&\b1}\N\N巨人拥有的特殊能力\N均是通过消耗肉体产生。\N超大型巨人释放出的热风也一样，\N是通过消耗肌肉组织而产生的，\N并不能无限使用。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}野兽巨人开始朝这边攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这里很快也会变成蜂窝的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}埃尔文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要是没有反击的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那就做败退的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}去把躺在那的艾伦叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}让艾伦带着你和其他几个人逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}至少要留几个生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}喂 马逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那不是你们负责的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你闭嘴 都没意义了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那么强大的调查兵团 瞬间就死光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你也明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}再怎么保护马匹都没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}根本没有人能骑着马回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}道理我都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}人类如果一直躲在墙内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}总有一天会被突然来袭的巨人吃干抹净
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}必须要有人冒着危险行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}需要有人能为了保护别人而牺牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}「谁是这样勇敢的士兵」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}听到这句话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我想到 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可是 没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们会以这种方式死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没想到我们会死得毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那么多人的牺牲都毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为什么会觉得只有自己是不同的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}让新兵和汉吉分队的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}骑上马分散逃离怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}以他们为诱饵 让艾伦带着你们逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}利威尔 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我去对付野兽巨人 吸引他的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不行 你根本没法靠近他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只要你和艾伦活着回去 就还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你不觉得吗 局势已经到这个地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们输得很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我甚至觉得谁都没法活着回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}前提是我们没有反击手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}难道还有办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为什么要阴沉着脸一言不发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}如果计划顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你应该可以干掉野兽巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但要牺牲这些新兵和我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不论如何 我们都会死伤殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 全军覆没的可能性要大得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}既然这样 我们也只能豁出性命去抓住胜机了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为此 要让那些年轻人去死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我要像大骗子一样对他们花言巧语一番
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我必须跑在最前面 不然他们根本不会往前冲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}然后我会第一个死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}再也没法知道地下室里有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我想就这样去地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我之所以能走到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就是因为坚信着这一天一定会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}坚信着 总有一天能验证我的猜想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我也无数次想 还不如死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我和父亲的梦想却还是在脑海里挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}而现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}答案就在触手可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}已经近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}但是 利威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你能看见我们的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}同伴们在看着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他们想知道自己献出的心脏现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}战斗还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这一切都只是我幼稚的幻想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}多亏了你 我们才能走到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我要选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}放弃梦想去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}把新兵带到地狱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我会收拾掉野兽巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}突击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我也没觉得他们会就这么放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}敢死队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我还以为他们会有更机灵点的办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就是现在 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}烟雾？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}信号枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要来了 移动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}接下来下达最后的作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}全体列队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}全体骑马进行突击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}目标是野兽巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}在目标看来 我们是绝好的靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们要看准目标投石的时机 一齐发射信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}尽可能降低投石的命中率
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们做诱饵吸引目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}利威尔士兵长趁机讨伐野兽巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}以上就是作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你要我一个人用立体机动接近野兽巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}野兽巨人周边可是空地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没有可以落脚的树木和房屋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不是有一排高度正合适的立体物站在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}通过巨人靠近目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}对野兽巨人发动奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}站在这不动也只会被飞来的碎石砸到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}立刻开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们这是要去送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}反正都是一死 还不如在战斗中死掉是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}反正都是死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不论是战死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}还是违背命令而死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}都毫无意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}全都毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不论拥有怎样的梦想和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不论过着怎样幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}都和被岩石打碎身体没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}结局都是死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那么人生是否没有意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}或者说 难道我们的出生就是毫无意义的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那些死去的同伴也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那些牺牲的士兵们也毫无意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那些士兵的意义 将由我们赋予
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那些勇敢的死者 那些可悲的死者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们之所以能这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是因为我们是生者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}将意义托付给下一个生者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这就是与这个残酷世界抗争的唯一手段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}士兵们 愤怒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}士兵们 咆哮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}士兵们 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为了献出心脏的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为了放弃梦想的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他们不停奔跑 直到一切都化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}在混乱和恐惧中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}下集 勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

